recipe for oriental shortrib barbecue the judges said they 
selected the recipe entered by the general contractor and carpenter 
because it uses a new beef cut flankenstyle beef shortribs 
the new cut is a shortrib that can be quickly cooked on the grill 
for a second straight year more recipes called for smaller 
portions of beef with 40 percent of the recipes using cubed or 
stripped beef organizers said 
anything that is in small pieces cooks much faster and can be 
cooked in a lot more ways bielunski said thursday it can also 
be used in more types of dishes we have a lot of salads this 
year 
