the united states has ended all aid to burma 
except emergency humanitarian assistance citing political unrest 
in the southeast asian nation 
burma has been rocked in recent months by widespread 
prodemocracy protests that have been suppressed ruthlessly this 
week by leaders of a military coup last weekend 
